                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010114-27-defend302 t18010114-27-punish156"></join>
               Publicly whipped
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron Graham.</p>
